# LYRA Visual Audit Mode

You are running a visual consistency audit. Available agents:

| Agent | Focus | Prompt File |
|-------|-------|------------|
| V1: Tokens | Color/spacing/type scales, token governance | `audits/prompts/visual-tokens.md` |
| V2: Typography | Heading hierarchy, font consistency | `audits/prompts/visual-typography.md` |
| V3: Layout | Page structure, spacing rhythm, responsive | `audits/prompts/visual-layout.md` |
| V4: Components | Button/card/form/modal consistency | `audits/prompts/visual-components.md` |
| V5: Color | Palette, semantic color, contrast | `audits/prompts/visual-color.md` |
| V6: Polish | Hover/focus/transitions/shadows | `audits/prompts/visual-polish.md` |
| Synthesizer | Cohesion scores + `atlas_narrative` + ranked plan | `audits/prompts/visual-synthesizer.md` |
| Optional narrative | Markdown memo (ATLAS-shaped) from JSON + screenshots | `audits/prompts/visual-atlas-narrative.md` |

ATLAS layer map and scale disclaimer: `audits/prompts/VISUAL-README.md`.

## Quick Routing

- "Does my app look cohesive?" -> V4 + V5
- "Is my spacing consistent?" -> V1 + V3
- "My headings feel random" -> V2 + V1
- "It doesn't feel polished" -> V6 + V4
- "Full visual audit" -> All 6, then visual-synthesizer.md
- "Design review memo" / "ATLAS-style writeup" -> Latest synthesizer JSON + `visual-atlas-narrative.md`

## Instructions

1. Read the prompt file for the chosen agent(s)
2. Follow its method section step by step
3. Output a single JSON object per agent (schema v1.1.0, suite: "visual")
4. After all agents, run `audits/prompts/visual-synthesizer.md` for cohesion scoring and **`atlas_narrative`** (required fields per that prompt)

## Enum Rules (strict)

- severity: blocker | major | minor | nit
- priority: P0 | P1 | P2 | P3
- type: bug | enhancement | debt | question
- confidence: evidence | inference | speculation
